snippet.textDisplay:
Just Spellbound. 
I think this song is gonna make on my fav songs list for year at least. I have always been the biggest fan of Kazi Nazrul’s Gazal to be more specific the tune of Nazrul’s gazal is majestic and listening "Bulbuli" for the first time and on a such voice made me so reminiscent of something beautiful that i m diving in slowly right now.
This is outstanding composition to tribute to our very own national poet the versatile Kazi Nazrul Islam.His lyrics are just masterclass and the tune is so soothing u just can't keep ur ears away from listening it.

Love to the Coke Studio Bangla Team for this amazing surprise. Listening it on repeat mood.♥️
